videos.description: Katie Lou Samelson steals the ball and Kia Nurse finishes on the other end with an and-1 layup.
videos.headline: UConn capitalizes on turnover

videos.description: Katie Lou Samuelson drains a 3-pointer from the top of the key, adding to UConn's 20-0 run to end the first quarter vs. Memphis.
videos.headline: Huskies end 1st quarter with 20-0 run

videos.description: The Huskies move the ball around and Napheesa Collier finds Katie Lou Samuelson wide open underneath the basket for a layup.
videos.headline: UConn throws off Memphis with ball movement

videos.description: Megan Walker drains a corner 3-pointer to punctuate Connecticut's win over Memphis.
videos.headline: Walker widens gap with corner 3-pointer
